commits.message: fixed bug with cells above grid (so spawn is moved back up) and fixed duplicate key warnings
replaced repeated grid looping with arrayPiece variable and sped up cleared row checking/clearing
added sonic drop in place of soft drop and made minor fixes to piece spawn and movement
add option to persist settings from current game
moved spawn down to avoid weird bug, made many various fixes
implemented gravity toggling and touch controls
implemented soft drop and lock delay
fixed bug from original code where only half of consecutive cleared rows would actually be cleared
update grid loader to always generate a new set during retry
